en_117680_0	The Telecommunication and Digital Infrastructure Minister Harin Fernando said that a special communication device would be introduced in the near future to enable parents to locate their children while children would be able to contact parents and police in an emergency.
en_117680_1	Addressing a media conference held in Colombo this morning, the minister stated steps would be taken to introduce this special device after considering the series of tragic incidents in the recent past.
